# Assets folder — images served from CDN (same as live site)

Images used in this project are loaded from Base44 CDN URLs in index.html and script.js.

To use local copies, download these into `assets/images/` and update paths:

- `desert-bg.png` — hero background
- `vessel.png` — desert sailing vessel
- `logo.png` — TAHWISA compass logo
- Experience card images (6 total)

Logo: `assets/logo/`
Icons: `assets/icons/` (SVG icons are inline in HTML)
